{"tid":2509544,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"放盤兩年！沙田第一城三房減價11%成交","createTime":"2021-04-29T13:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T05:48:43.000Z","uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c51604b9125f2165b3568aa6cf987c12844a646b","tid":2509544,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"二手速遞｜放盤兩年！沙田第一城三房減價11%成交 AM730 Apr 29 2021 - 10:14<br />\n<br />\n指標屋苑交投熾熱，頻錄得成交個案。世紀21奇豐物業愉翠苑分行經理楊麗娟表示，沙田第一城17座低層E室，實用面積約451方呎，屬三房兩廳間隔，座向東南望內園景觀。單位放盤2年，原叫價780萬元，最終減價85萬或約11%，以695萬元沽出，實用面積呎價約15,410元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2014年9月以460萬元購入單位，持貨至今將單位轉手帳面獲利235萬元，單位期內升值約51%。<br />\n<br />\n「文章版權為新傳媒集團所擁有，原文請按： <a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/273699/?utm_campaign=copy」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F273699%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dcopy%E3%80%8D&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=04d4ab9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/273699/?utm_campaign=copy」</a>"},{"pid":"eeec91934300007781b8cd0ecb81faee1914452b","tid":2509544,"uid":19927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce780c2b9efc87fd58baf1015d35304b6ba2445","tid":2509544,"uid":144090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌, 睇番成交原來又係差唔多市價"},{"pid":"299fcdea694917e5aa635a7135deb947340f2b53","tid":2509544,"uid":54351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"451 呎有3房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cc35af9a676dcdcef75eb49d043a76d8ac2949","tid":2509544,"uid":143386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"299fcdea694917e5aa635a7135deb94